'''哈莉·奎茵·史密斯'''（{{lang-en|Harley Quinn Smith}}，{{bd|1999年|6月29日}}）是一位美國女演員，為導演[[凱文·史密斯|凱文·史密斯]]和女演員{{link-en|珍妮佛·史瓦爾巴赫·史密斯|Jennifer Schwalbach Smith}}的女兒。

==早期生活==
哈莉·奎茵·史密斯出生於[[紐澤西州|紐澤西州]]的{{link-en|雷德班克 (紐澤西州)|Red Bank, New Jersey|雷德班克}}。父親[[凱文·史密斯|凱文·史密斯]]是知名導演、編劇、監製、演員和漫畫作家，而母親{{link-en|珍妮佛·史瓦爾巴赫·史密斯|Jennifer Schwalbach Smith}}則是名演員。她的名字是父親取自[[蝙蝠俠|蝙蝠俠]]的反派角色[[哈莉·奎茵|哈莉·奎茵]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ew.com/article/2016/01/31/suicide-squad-harley-quinn-bat-kevin-smith-daughter|title=Kevin Smith gifts Harley Quinn's Suicide Squad bat to his daughter, Harley Quinn|publisher=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]]|first=Nick|last=Romano|date=January 31, 2016|accessdate=May 29, 2016|archive-date=2018-11-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181121120651/https://ew.com/article/2016/01/31/suicide-squad-harley-quinn-bat-kevin-smith-daughter/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。她與[[強尼·戴普|強尼·戴普]]的女兒[[莉莉-蘿絲·戴普|莉莉-蘿絲·戴普]]是好友。

==職業生涯==
史密斯出演的首部電影為父親執導的《[[白爛賤客|白爛賤客]]》，當時她還只是個年幼的小孩<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/johnny-depp-kevin-smiths-daughters-745898|title=Johnny Depp and Kevin Smith's Daughters Debut First Image of 'Yoga Hosers' (Exclusive)|author=Pamela McClintock|date=4 November 2014|work=The Hollywood Reporter|accessdate=2016-09-06|archive-date=2016-08-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160829221252/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/johnny-depp-kevin-smiths-daughters-745898|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2004年，她在《[[紐澤西愛未眠|紐澤西愛未眠]]》中飾演一名未掛名的小角色，她於兩年後在喜劇片《[[瘋狂店員2|瘋狂店員2]]》中演出<ref>{{cite web|url=http://mentalfloss.com/article/58721/15-things-you-probably-didnt-know-about-clerks-ii|title=15 Things You Probably Didn’t Know About Clerks II|work=Mental Floss|accessdate=2016-09-06|archive-date=2016-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160921194838/http://mentalfloss.com/article/58721/15-things-you-probably-didnt-know-about-clerks-ii|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年，史密斯在驚悚片《{{le|人型海象|Tusk (2014 film)}}》中飾演一名小角色，之後她又於2016年的《[[瑜珈魯蛇|瑜珈魯蛇]]》同樣出演該角<ref>{{cite web|last1=Smith|first1=Kevin|title=I love this so much. This is from the end credits of #YogaHosers. Get ready to face a monster moose, @harleyquinnnn_ & @lilyrose_depp!|url=https://facebook.com/YesThatKevinSmith/photos/a.77596326929.88348.6985046929/10152814889886930/?type=1&source=48&_ft_=top_level_post_id.10152814889886930|website=Facebook|accessdate=12 June 2015|archive-date=2019-12-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191215222413/https://facebook.com/YesThatKevinSmith/photos/a.77596326929.88348.6985046929/10152814889886930/?type=1&source=48&_ft_=top_level_post_id.10152814889886930|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2016年1月，宣布將於電視喜劇《''Hollyweed''》中參演<ref name=Harley-Quinn-Smith-Hollyweed>{{cite news|last1=Smith|first1=Kevin|title=HOLLYWEED! This is a project we quietly shot last week in which I act with dialogue. To better understand what this means to me, here's a text I sent my kid after I finished putting her scenes together (she plays my daughter in the show)...|url=https://facebook.com/YesThatKevinSmith/posts/10153205572436930|accessdate=26 January 2016|publisher=''[[Facebook|Facebook]]''|date=January 22, 2016}}</ref>。

